**FormGrid** (`src/components/responsive/form-grid.tsx`) вЂ” new lightweight utility that provides responsive grid columns (1-col mobile, 2-col desktop at `sm:` breakpoint).

**Registration form migration** вЂ” replaced the stacked `space-y-4` layout with `FormGrid columns={2}`:
- **Side-by-side on desktop**: fullName + email, phone + designation, city + age
- **Full-width** (`col-span-full`): specialty, organization
- **Mobile**: everything stacks to single column automatically

**Results**: 13/13 tests passing, no type errors in our files, no build errors from our changes.
